@lbindex Step
@kindex F5
Continue running your program until control reaches a different source
line, then stop it and return control to @DDD{} (@key{F5}).
@xref{Resuming Execution}, for details.

@item Step Instruction
@lbindex Step Instruction
@kindex Shift+F5
Execute one machine instruction, then stop and return to @DDD{}
(@key{Shift+F5}).  @xref{Machine Code Execution}, for details.

@item Next
@lbindex Next
@kindex F6
Continue to the next source line in the current (innermost) stack frame
